{"tid":1909860,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍Wetland Seasons Park II批預售 新地：月底前開售","createTime":"2020-03-04T09:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T06:20:13.000Z","uid":159234,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e4792ca65ade91d57edac03055a4475d506edb00","tid":1909860,"uid":159234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:11:45.000Z","msg":"新盤氣氛回暖，多個全新盤陸續推售，而新地旗下天水圍Wetland Seasons Park II（Wetland Lot No.&nbsp;34&nbsp;Development發展項目第2期）剛獲批預售，料本月底前推售。<br />\n新地副董事總經理雷霆回應地產站查詢指，美國減息有機會減輕本港置業者的供樓負擔，當然有利樓市，而集團旗下Wetland Seasons Park II剛獲得預售樓花同意書，樓書亦接近完成，有機會本月底前開售。<br />\n資料顯示，Wetland Seasons Park II提供699伙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n天水圍豪宅又黎啦   有冇人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d54c051076e112b8d651d7405f35152bdb81f0","tid":1909860,"uid":152507,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:12:50.000Z","msg":"搶呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698d4eddf632cc4011687743062dd0a2bda04507","tid":1909860,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:27:39.000Z","msg":"折左幾錢?"},{"pid":"831f36fedf2b487ff1285bfb290da518b732a42c","tid":1909860,"uid":305694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:32:48.000Z","msg":"二期價單會加幾多%？"},{"pid":"8959a71cb7fddbfd942af62f0e520979c31be29b","tid":1909860,"uid":63952,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:43:40.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，又成班人逼喺ICC?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0f8b29a2b4ad82ec0dd7a897f1b302ff4d78da","tid":1909860,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"恆大棍龍灣2期加價"},{"pid":"b0a1200eaa6d0dfb113a6494f8a3b8f9a4e5a8f3","tid":1909860,"uid":200167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc